@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.exp(v1 + 0.74)) + wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.83)))
    tmp = wp.cos((0.84 * wp.exp(tmp + 0.62)))
    v1 = (0.23 / 0.99)
    tmp = v2
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.cos(wp.exp(v0 + 0.73)))
    v0 = (tmp - (v2 - (v0 + 0.30 - v0 + 0.46)))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.cos(0.23))
    data[tid] = v0
